---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — AB Brothers Construction"
  description="Privacy Policy for AB Brothers Construction Inc. How we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
>

  <section class="pp-hero section--surface">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-dim pp-date">Last updated: 5/26/2025</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pp-body">
    <div class="wrap wrap--narrow">
      <div class="pp-content">

        <p>At AB Brothers Construction Inc., your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect the personal information you provide through our website, lead forms, and other interactions with our business.</p>

        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect the following types of personal information:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Name</li>
          <li>Email address</li>
          <li>Phone number</li>
          <li>Address (if provided in form)</li>
          <li>Project interests or details (if submitted in a message or inquiry)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>This information is typically collected when you:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Submit a contact form or lead form on our website</li>
          <li>Call or email us directly</li>
          <li>Interact with one of our ads (e.g., Google Ads lead form extensions)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Respond to your inquiries or service requests</li>
          <li>Schedule consultations or estimates</li>
          <li>Provide project-related updates or information</li>
          <li>Send occasional promotional or follow-up emails (you can opt out at any time)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not sell or share your information with third parties for their own marketing purposes.</p>

        <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>We may share your personal information with:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Trusted service providers who help us operate our business (e.g., CRM platforms, email services)</li>
          <li>Legal authorities if required by law</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure.</p>

        <h2>5. Your Choices</h2>
        <p>You may contact us at any time to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Request access to the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction or deletion of your information</li>
          <li>Opt out of any future communications</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. Google Advertising Disclosure</h2>
        <p>We may use Google Ads and other digital advertising services to promote our business. These services may collect information about your interaction with our ads. For more information on how Google uses data, visit: <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google's advertising policies</a>.</p>

        <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us:</p>
        <address>
          AB Brothers Construction Inc.<br />
          Mount Lebanon, PA<br />
          Phone: <a href="tel:4123788115">(412) 378-8115</a><br />
          Email: <a href="mailto:abbrotherspgh@gmail.com">abbrotherspgh@gmail.com</a>
        </address>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .pp-hero {
    padding-block: 3rem 2rem;
  }

  .pp-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
  }

  .pp-date {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .pp-body {
    padding-block: var(--section-y);
  }

  .pp-content {
    color: var(--cream-dim);
    line-height: 1.75;

    & h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: var(--cream);
    }

    & p {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    & ul {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    & li {
      list-style: disc;
      margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
      font-size: 0.9375rem;
    }

    & a {
      color: var(--copper);
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-underline-offset: 2px;
    }

    & a:hover {
      color: var(--copper-light);
    }

    & address {
      font-style: normal;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--cream);
    }
  }
</style>
